scripts.git: node -e "const readline = require('readline'); const { exec } = require('child_process'); const rl = readline.createInterface({ input: process.stdin, output: process.stdout }); rl.question('Enter commit message: ', (message) => { rl.question('Enter branch name: ', (branch) => { exec(`git add . && git commit -m \"${message}\" && git push -u origin ${branch}`, (err, stdout, stderr) => { if (err) { console.error(`Error: ${err.message}`); } else { console.log(stdout); } rl.close(); }); }); });"
